1591 St. Nicholas Avenue (formerly Eleventh Avenue) at N.W. corner of 190th Street. The view is west on the north side of 190th Street. This is one of the early apartment houses of the Fort
George section; it was built around 1914.
October 26, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
